OL,3,CWoman who had life-saving heart
OL,4,Csurgery urges people to become organ
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,FA student from Stockport says she
OL,8,Fwould never have met her "beautiful
OL,9,Fbaby nephew" if it wasn't for a life
OL,10,Fsaving heart surgery.
OL,12,FPoppy Wilson, 21, would have gone into
OL,13,Fheart failure had she not received a
OL,14,Fvalve replacement in June 2025.
OL,16,FPoppy's now joining calls for more
OL,17,Fpeople to sign up as a donor, after
OL,18,Fthe NHS Blood and Transplant (NHSBT)
OL,19,Fservice raised alarms about a drop in
OL,20,Fthe number of heart valves donated for
OL,21,Fsurgeries.
