OL,7,FThe NHS could not supply around 20% of
OL,8,Fheart valve requests from hospitals
OL,9,Flast year, according to new figures
OL,10,Ffrom NHS Blood and Transplant (NHSBT).
OL,12,FMs Wilson, who studied history at
OL,13,FManchester Metropolitan University,
OL,14,Fwas born with congenital heart disease
OL,15,Fand needed a valve replacement after
OL,16,Fher own aortic heart valve became
OL,17,Fleaky and narrow.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
