OL,3,CWoman who had life-saving heart
OL,4,Csurgery urges people to become organ
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,FShe said how grateful she was to her
OL,8,Fdonor's family, after she had her
OL,9,Fsurgery at Liverpool Heart and Chest
OL,10,FHospital.
OL,12,FShe said: "I went for lunch with my
OL,13,Fmum where we had to walk up a steep
OL,14,Fhill. I began to cry because I could
OL,15,Fnot believe I did not feel chest pain,
OL,16,Fpalpitations or breathlessness- I'd
OL,17,Fnever felt like that before.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
