OL,3,CWoman who had life-saving heart
OL,4,Csurgery urges people to become organ
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,F"A month after the operation I got to
OL,8,Fmeet my beautiful baby nephew. I would
OL,9,Fnot have been able to do that without
OL,10,Fthe heart valve.
OL,12,F"I get so emotional thinking about the
OL,13,Fdonor and the donor family. I can't
OL,14,Fput into words how grateful I am. It's
OL,15,Foverwhelming.
OL,17,F"I would encourage people to donate
OL,18,Fbecause my donor absolutely changed my
OL,19,Flife."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
