OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,FHeart valve replacements are needed
OL,8,Fwhen a person's heart valve is
OL,9,Fdamaged, diseased or defective.
OL,11,FPatients include adults, whose heart
OL,12,Fvalves can begin to narrow or leak,
OL,13,Fand for children with genetic heart
OL,14,Fdisorders.
OL,16,FOfficials say the shortage of valves
OL,17,Fis continuing this year, following a
OL,18,Fdip in the number of hearts donated to
OL,19,Fheart valve banks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
