OL,4,Csurgery urges people to become organ
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,FNHSBT figures show 600 hearts were
OL,8,Fdonated in 2021, while just 368 were
OL,9,Fdonated in 2024.
OL,11,FJackie Brander, head of operations for
OL,12,Ftissue donation at NHS Blood and
OL,13,FTransplant said: "Heart valves can be
OL,14,Fespecially important for babies born
OL,15,Fwith genetic heart defects.
OL,17,F"But the reality is we are just not
OL,18,Fgetting enough donations to meet
OL,19,Fdemand. We think there are several
OL,20,Freasons why heart valve donation has
OL,21,Fdecreased.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
