OL,7,FProfessor Attilio Lotto, a congenital
OL,8,Fcardiac surgeon from Liverpool, said:
OL,9,F"Every donated heart valve represents
OL,10,Fnot just a gift, but a second chance
OL,11,Fat life.
OL,13,F"While many people are familiar with
OL,14,Fthe idea of donating organs such as
OL,15,Fkidneys, liver, or lungs, fewer
OL,16,Frealise that donating heart valves and
OL,17,Ftissues after death can also transform
OL,18,Flives."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
